### Get all tasks
GET http://localhost:3000/api/tasks
Accept: application/json

###

### Get a single task by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/api/tasks/1
Accept: application/json

###

### Create a new task
POST http://localhost:3000/api/tasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Sample Task from request.http",
  "description": "This is a test task created via request.http"
}

###

### Update a task by ID
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/tasks/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Updated Task Title",
  "description": "Updated description"
}

###

### Mark a task as completed
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/tasks/1/complete
Accept: application/json

###

### Mark a task as pending
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/tasks/1/pending
Accept: application/json

###

### Delete a task by ID
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/tasks/1
Accept: application/json

###

### Get task statistics
GET http://localhost:3000/api/tasks/stats
Accept: application/json

###

### Filter tasks (e.g., only pending, limit 5)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/tasks?completed=false&limit=5
Accept: application/json
